    Scope and Contents
The Library Support staff Committee (1977-78) file contains agendas, minutes, evaluations, and correspondences.  Also included are Student Employment (1978), Support Staff By-Laws (1978) and Library News (1978) and documents referring to search for ISL (Instructional Services Librarian) 1977.  The Support Staff committee's main goal was to promote better communication between the library support staff, library faculty and library administrators and  provide input for the support staff.  
  
